olive oil
1 Sourdough Loaf
1 bag baby broccoli
½ lemon
1 packet pine nuts
1 packet basil pesto
1 packet mayonnaise
1 bag spinach & rocket mix
1 packet cold smoked salmon

• Toast or grill sourdough to your liking, then tear into chunks. Drizzle with olive oil and season
• Trim and halve baby broccoli. Cut lemon into wedges

• In a large frying pan, heat a drizzle of oil over medium-high heat
• Cook baby broccoli and pine nuts, tossing, until tender, 5-6 mins

• In a bowl, combine sourdough, baby broccoli, spinach & rocket mix, pesto, a squeeze of lemon juice and a drizzle of oil. Season
• Plate up salad and top with salmon. Drizzle over mayonnaise
• Serve with remaining lemon wedges